**Title:** Trigger Onboarding Emails by Subscription Tier

**As a** marketing manager,  
**I want** new subscription customers to receive onboarding emails tailored to their chosen tier,  
**So that** they get a more personalized experience and reduce refund rates.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- [ ] First-time subscription orders trigger Klaviyo flow based on tier
- [ ] Mini-tier receives 1 welcome email
- [ ] Essentials and Deluxe receive multi-step onboarding flow with product use tips and upsell opportunities
